Package com.example.c195

Class DBAccessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.c195.DBAccessor
  • public final class DBAccessor
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to abstract the Database functions from the controller. I wanted to build everything separately, test that it is working first, and then change the code here to actually pull data from the database.
